0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3f81095658354c675a6768e174f9fdc0db43fd","tid":2032710,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38cd56a25efb9895f10552b3430aeae3becac969","tid":2032710,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:40:23.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登紅色五毛分化警告</span><br />\n宜家班死五毛<span style=\"color: red;\">除左用鬥黃進行分化，仲用扮演移民/留守派黎進行分化</span>，大家請保持獨立思考<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後大家要幫手簽個聯署支持BNO平權救手足</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=7735e8c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"299e15a359d3626229359bb315ce40e73120cd7e","tid":2032710,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e68f7162145dcce82c164698d30420d6f2fbc6","tid":2032710,"uid":300952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:40:42.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"26cbe9c661740298d8c1fbe726b33d3514649529","tid":2032710,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:40:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e62c00a09c96599bfedad2dc355e4ea119077d0","tid":2032710,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c92f26f8d36c6b31239ba0f2aa3ddb84973bb5c9","tid":2032710,"uid":258345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9b15a24290ff096c728a674f61e15a8a69021c","tid":2032710,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"234ab481d01620cc9f3d1a7b5b477d3c103fd4d0","tid":2032710,"uid":280475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:43:38.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"bbbfa00ffd497ed6f13e011e5cb0